{"tid":1224321,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"暫緩即係遙控㩒咗pause 隨時㩒返Play 我哋要stop!","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T16:04:13.000Z","uid":221265,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3ab29b168eb9bcf670910ffc45859b3f64be29","tid":1224321,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"暫緩即係遙控㩒咗pause 隨時㩒返Play 我哋要stop!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPause完好快play<br />\n<br />\n同屋企人解釋！"},{"pid":"ce6916ae2a0e34350eafdf2e87c068062295a0ff","tid":1224321,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都係要撤回！<br />\n林鄭係聽民意既話 唔該你撤回！<br />\n<br />\n暫緩係絕對唔收貨！<br />\n<br />\n1. 係撤回 唔係暫緩<br />\n103萬人以至612 全部都係撤回<br />\n如果佢話係尊重民意而暫緩 根本唔汲取教訓 無聽民意！<br />\n講暫緩既 都係啲建制派既人<br />\n不撤回 不收貨<br />\n想用暫緩俾啲甜頭香港人根本係一種侮辱！<br />\n<br />\n2. 暫緩根本無意思<br />\n你估問題係修法度咩？<br />\n一日你未搞掂中国既法治同人權水平<br />\n一日你未搞掂政府賣港既形象<br />\n你點改都係無人會信 根本係信任問題！<br />\n3000名法律界人士咁有權威都話要反修例 撤回送中<br />\n憑乜野覺得暫緩再同人解釋會令人信？<br />\n<br />\n6月16照出街 講多次我地既訴求係撤回而唔係暫緩！<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣叫讓步！<br />\n<br />\n你同我撤回完同我放埋啲被捕義士先叫讓步！同追究唒啲黑警先叫讓步！<br />\n暫你老母！<br />\n緩你老母！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 唔好被騙！<br />\n<br />\n6月16日再遊行<br />\n四大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回引渡方案<br />\n2. 釋放被捕義士<br />\n3. 追究暴力黑警<br />\n4. 政官問責下台<br />\n<br />\n得一個暫緩點收貨？<br />\n點對得住受傷既示威者？<br />\n警察做野可以無後果？<br />\n政官搞壇咁既野都無事？<br />\n<br />\n6月16日 不撤不散"},{"pid":"1a0db7c8371e5055d6da4ffb7bce535778f87851","tid":1224321,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>[騙徒手法 層出不窮] 政府反擊 唔好中計 <br />\n<br />\n濕鳩政府做濕鳩嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋嘅game plan同五年前一撚樣</span> 又係慣常技倆 軟攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住拖得就拖 襯機會軟化中間派 <br />\n你一拖就少人<br />\n人一少就無人衝<br />\n最後一大班人俾人拉，咩都得唔到，又輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家一定要set Deadline</span> 唔係就升級 絕不接受暫緩<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫你老母<br />\n撤回</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fa9381500a0ca58a70854060d64169b31ed2ead4","tid":1224321,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jppYPA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jppYPA.png&h=3bf6d7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔要pause<br />\n<br />\n要stop!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2500229dd7a52c891eb37f063fd8cc2f00c059bc","tid":1224321,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ee989f6bb4b0c77f3f7c9ee0d261959ec3fc76b8","tid":1224321,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻你<br />\n麻煩入嚟幫推<br />\n因為「暫緩」係一個好撚難聽嘅詞語<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好以為「暫緩」係階段勝利  其實係暗地裡捉緊人 一定要盡早撤回！冇得拖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b236f91086869ed2511bbf90bddc075e41dd7b5","tid":1224321,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"facebook有個remote圖，我地係要Eject"},{"pid":"2c6ae48218feaa1415866839b21d22d7f43ecf0b","tid":1224321,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n不要pauce<br />\n<br />\n都老嘢唔識分<br />\n<br />\n用依個approach 啱啦"},{"pid":"b9056bf044423d917d6dde975b5a186eda14968d","tid":1224321,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"你哋做埋圖?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLMwUGK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th